description:
LONDONTOWN LONDONTOWN! As the famous quote goes "When a man is tired of London, he is tired of life for there is in London all that life can afford". And same goes for its sprawling and incredibly diverse food scene! The home of Big Ben, Buckingham Palace, and Tower Bridge has been at the forefront of pop culture, art, and music but it is the food that'll keep us coming back to this great city!

In this video, we highlight all 15 places we ate at in London. From classic fish and chips, obscene Sunday roasts, comforting English Breakfasts, afternoon teas and even Indian and Chinese food, London has got so many great spots to explore and eat at.

This of course is not an exhaustive list but we hope you still find our experiences useful when you plan your own London food adventure!

Enjoy!

Our full London vlogs:
Is this London's Best English Breakfast? | British Food Tour ft. Jellied Eels and Greggs!
https://youtu.be/QhuQ-1MsqNg

BRITISH FOOD TOUR in LONDON | Fish & Chips, Bangers & Pies!
https://youtu.be/HEAL57jB2o8

London's Best Food Market! | Borough Market Tour + Afternoon Tea,  Indian Food, and St. Paul's!
https://youtu.be/KWoKkFfavYo

Trying the ULTIMATE SUNDAY ROAST in LONDON! | Blacklock Shoreditch
https://youtu.be/-IQ8pSrmRGI
